<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ἀκυλίῳ Καπιτωλείνῳ 

    <lb n="2"/>τῷ κρατίστῳ <expan>ἐπιστρ<ex cert="high">ατήγῳ</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="3"/>παρὰ Σαραπίωνος <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἱ</hi>έ-

    <lb n="4"/>ρακος ἀπ᾽ Ὀξυρύγχων 

    <lb n="5"/>πόλεως ἐπιμελητοῦ 

    <lb n="6"/>Σαραπείου φυλῶν καὶ τῶν 

    <lb n="7"/>ἄλλων <hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ερῶν <sic>καὶ</sic> τῆς 

    <lb n="8"/>πόλεως. ἐνέτυχόν 

    <lb n="9"/>σοι, κύριε, διὰ βιβλιδίου 

    <lb n="10"/><choice><corr>ἀξιοῦντός</corr><sic>εξιουντος</sic></choice> σου καὶ ὑπέ-

    <lb n="11"/>σχου ὥστε ἀνάπεμψαι 

    <lb n="12"/>τὰ βιβλίδια καὶ μέχρι τού-

    <lb n="13"/>του οὐκ ἀνεδόθη μοι 

    <lb n="14"/>περί τε ὕβρε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ως</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἣ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear>-

    <lb n="15"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μοὶ</unclear> ἐγένετο ὑπὸ Πλουτί-

    <lb n="16"/>ωνος Διονυσοδώρου καὶ 

    <lb n="17"/>τοῦ γαμβροῦ αὐτοῦ. ἐνέτυ-

    <lb n="18"/>χον δὲ καὶ Ἡρακλείδῃ 

    <lb n="19"/>βασιλικῷ γραμματεῖ δια-

    <lb n="20"/>δεχομένῳ καὶ τὰ κατὰ 

    <lb n="21"/>τὴν στρατηγίαν, καὶ ἀ-

    <lb n="22"/>νήγκασεν ἑνὶ τῶν πε-

    <lb n="23"/>ρὶ αὐτὸν ὑπηρετῶν 

    <lb n="24"/>Θράσυλλον <choice><corr>ἐπιδεῖν</corr><sic>εφιδειν</sic></choice> τὴν 

    <lb n="25"/>περὶ ἐμὲ διάθεσιν περὶ 

    <lb n="26"/>τῆς γεγενημένης μοι 

    <lb n="27"/>ὕβρεως, καὶ προσφώνη-

    <lb n="28"/>σις <hi rend="diaeresis">ἰ</hi>ατροῦ ἐπηκολούθη-

    <lb n="29"/>σεν περὶ ὧν εἶχον τότε 

    <lb n="30"/>τραυμάτων. οὐ μόνον 

    <lb n="31"/>ἐμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὲ</unclear> ἀλλὰ καὶ τὸν υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>όν 

    <lb n="32"/>μου καὶ τὴν τροφὸν αὐ-

    <lb n="33"/>τοῦ Ἡρᾶν ᾐκίσατο αὐ-

    <lb n="34"/>τοὺς πληγαῖς ἕν<unclear cert="low" reason="undefined">εκα</unclear>

    <lb n="35"/>κληρονομίας <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>[<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> <choice><corr>ἐν]-

    <lb n="36"/>δομενίας</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εν</supplied>δομενειας</sic></choice> ἧς κατέλει-

    <lb n="37"/>ψεν τῇ Ἡρᾶτι ὁ ἀδελφὸς 

    <lb n="38"/>αὐτῆς Σαραπίων μετὰ 

    <lb n="39"/>τελευτὴν αὐτοῦ καὶ ἐδη-

    <lb n="40"/>μοσιώθη διὰ τοῦ ἀρχιδικα-

    <lb n="41"/>στοῦ τὸ γράμμα ὥστε αὐ-

    <lb n="42"/>τὴν εἶναι κληρονόμον. 

    <lb n="43"/>οὕτως οὖν αὐθάδως χρη-

    <lb n="44"/>σάμενος κωμήτης ὢν 

    <lb n="45"/>ἐπῆλθεν <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice>. ἐπὶ σὲ 

    <lb n="46"/>κατέφυγον τὸν πάντων 

    <lb n="47"/>σωτῆρα καὶ εὐεργέτην 

    <lb n="48"/>ἀκοῦσαί μου πρὸς αὐτόν. 

    <lb n="49"/>οὐδεμία βία γείνεται 

    <lb n="50"/>ἐν τοῖς εὐτυχεστάτοις 

    <lb n="51"/>τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν Αὐρηλίου 

    <lb n="52"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Ἀ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ντωνείνο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καίσ</unclear>αρος τοῦ 

    <lb n="53"/><gap extent="12" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">η</unclear> ἐπιστρα 

    <lb n="54"/><gap extent="12" reason="lost" unit="character"/>νμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εν</unclear> 

    <lb n="55"/><gap extent="13" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">η</unclear>μα </ab></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 170</date></p></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">31</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">2563</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">16886</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">31</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">2563</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;31;2563" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">149</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.16886" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH010df7340e7fe3dd5d53bc13"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>